Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会竭尽全力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.55,0:02:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也必须告诉您 现在这种状态持续下去会有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经联络过我的父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是会尽快赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他需要联络的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水濑 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师也会尽一份力的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.81,0:02:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么的事话立刻联络我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:02:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 一定会得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 病情并没有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 请用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前的状态我想大概还会持续一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情有变的话会马上联络您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请暂回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.14,0:03:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能的话 请待在立即就能联络到的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉呢 丢下你不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子一定饿了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.55,0:04:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微吃一点吧 从昨天起就什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.59,0:04:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我说想吃草莓蛋糕 妈妈才…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.17,0:04:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去学校了 要向老师报告各种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书包也还扔在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物我放这里了 要好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在治疗中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水濑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 我能帮上忙的地方尽管叫就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的路上去了一下医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病情似乎没什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在里面的吧 我进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 书包也带回来了 能不能开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在… 那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话想和你说
