Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 如果有这家伙在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气氛会不会热闹一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 看到雪兔你想起了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直都记得的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个时候我在哭泣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起了真琴的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有舞的事情 以及名雪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 仍还忘记着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 我去医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物给你放这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 平静下来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.48,0:09:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我谁都不想见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一个人呆着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了呢 名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的食物好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 我做的和秋子阿姨做的比起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算这样一直自责下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨一定会得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位我行我素的秋子阿姨怎么可能就这样走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹会发生的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都和妈妈在一起的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知多少年 在这个小镇 在这个家相依为命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.90,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道爸爸的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因为有妈妈在 所以一点儿都不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都努力走过来了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而却因为我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是孤单一人的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.36,0:10:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么孤单一人 学校里不是有很多朋友的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香里 北川 还有田径部的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不就在你身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年间…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.85,0:11:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已经忘记了我的你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.16,0:11:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连回信都没写过一次的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都有好好读过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为什么回信都没有 我还以为是不是没收到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前重逢的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和祐一的相见 我其实非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.88,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕你会不会忘记了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起七年之前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒假的最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站前离别时的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只雪兔 真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能原谅我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是…过去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 能不能让我一起待在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一直都是和妈妈在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不是还有我吗」真说得出口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一直都淡忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.91,0:13:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在很久以前也有发生过这样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人受了重伤 我却什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.66,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由那家伙 一定生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君 迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是可以随时上学的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为赔礼 给你带吃的来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的准备已经做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去管了 今天是最后一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是最后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是约定好还要见面的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经约定好总有一天会在这里重逢的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 约定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来的时候向你介绍我的表妹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.76,0:14:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们一定会很要好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 偶很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的景色也很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都看着相同景色 你也真不会厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 再稍等一会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话 我马上带你去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 真的好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.32,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 所以别说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶很擅长爬树的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不到痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会痛了就说明绝对没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用动也没关系 我会带你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能动的话就没法玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会和偶一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有东西要送给亚由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心 约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾手指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手动不了的话 就没办法勾手指呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶…是个笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这样就能勾手指了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好了哦 亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 不勾好的话就不是勾手指了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快勾起手来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一起勾的话就不是勾手指了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.59,0:17:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相泽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心所以过来看看 出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？ 什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名雪拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 相泽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.77,0:18:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.84,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一直待着的话 能去到她那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.05,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 打开这个看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是叫发夹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.04,0:21:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后你说要还给你偶也不会还的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不是就算你说要还给我 我也不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 下次见祐一君的时候 偶就戴着这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约定好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了声音的嘈杂脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.10,0:23:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素不相识的人 不断穿梭在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.56,0:23:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会留意到那个孤单地坐在上长椅上的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等待着什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一个明知不会来的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.90,0:24:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一个明知再也见不到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.00,0:24:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知过了多少年 不知过了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.36,0:24:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶一直在等待着
